86
00:04:12,083 --> 00:04:12,541
Hey.

87
00:04:12,791 --> 00:04:13,416
Found it.

88
00:04:13,416 --> 00:04:14,291
I found it already.

89
00:04:16,166 --> 00:04:16,583
Oh.

90
00:04:17,041 --> 00:04:18,166
Found it.

91
00:04:18,708 --> 00:04:19,166
Okay.

92
