106
00:04:41,083 --> 00:04:41,458
Mm-hmm.

107
00:04:42,291 --> 00:04:43,166
Thank you.

108
00:04:44,916 --> 00:04:45,291
Oh.

109
00:04:46,041 --> 00:04:46,666
By the way.

110
00:04:47,041 --> 00:04:48,166
Actually, I came to Phayao...

111
00:04:48,166 --> 00:04:51,083
