180
00:09:04,416 --> 00:09:05,958
Then you be my guide.

181
00:09:08,291 --> 00:09:09,458
Well...

182
00:09:09,833 --> 00:09:10,291
Uh...

183
00:09:10,708 --> 00:09:11,541
I...

184
00:09:11,666 --> 00:09:12,791
