226
00:13:02,291 --> 00:13:02,666
Mmm

227
00:13:44,791 --> 00:13:47,083
This Meilin I just met...

228
00:13:47,416 --> 00:13:48,666
The me in her drawing...

229
00:13:49,083 --> 00:13:50,041
